{"tid":1676540,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【勇武要小心】有人想搞大裝修範圍","createTime":"2019-10-26T13:51:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-26T14:17:17.000Z","uid":278656,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5e0414710323925168f9ffdd5b96d189633fbfa1","tid":1676540,"uid":278656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T13:51:05.000Z","msg":"連續2星期有人製造事端，意圖令勇武擴大裝修範圍<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">第1個星期：</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">Jimmy被襲，連登即有人吹風搞南亞人／裝修南亞店鋪</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">第2個星期：</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">有人有組織插贜嫁禍譚仔，連登亦即有人吹雞要裝修譚仔</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">第3個星期：</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">待續......</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">建議：</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">制定清晰既裝修共識（如以咩證據同程度為準），以免再被輕易帶風。譚仔今次係好彩在佢地回應實在同及時。</span>"},{"pid":"fd77636b13010a97ffeb1ac3bd04d78faff2d8bf","tid":1676540,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T13:52:06.000Z","msg":"【黃色經濟】有個傻仔整咗個黃藍商鋪認證平台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eqgeNS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eqgeNS</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f15b7fa6deb17fe0a08df80ccdcfc299f0577365","tid":1676540,"uid":274538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T13:52:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XbLsc66.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXbLsc66.jpg&h=59b39c34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j9Vf6r7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj9Vf6r7.jpg&h=d42fe672&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TFJpZM8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTFJpZM8.jpg&h=85c40953&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BgKwEM9.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.